# VinMarkdown

This is a fairly faithful port of Craig Chockenberry's [MarkdownAttributedString](https://github.com/chockenberry/MarkdownAttributedString).

I needed some enhancements made to the original MarkdownAttributedString for [Zavala](https://github.com/vincode-io/Zavala). Because I was
struggling with the Objective-C in MarkdownAttributedString, I had [Claude](https://claude.ai) translate it to Swift. It was also supposed
to use [swift-markdown](https://github.com/apple/swift-markdown.git) for parsing and emitting. Claude and I even discussed this and agreed
together to use swift-markdown. Claude didn't use it.

You can consider this project to be a Swift fork of MarkdownAttributedString with some stuff specific to Zavala that may or may not work
with what you are doing. You are probably better off using the original MarkdownAttributedString than this project. It is production
proven and I haven't gotten my fingers into it.
